nc -znvw1 can scan ports
NETCAT - SCANNING :: nc [Options] [Target IP] [Target Port(s)] -z : Port scanning mode i.e. zero I/O mode -v : Be verbose [use twice -vv to be more verbose] -n : do not resolve ip addresses 
-w1 : Set time out value to 1 -u : To switch to UDP nc -zvnwl IP port (can be multple)
